    "body": "It seems in #5728 had been given some clarifications especially for the 2nd example\r\n\r\nI've checked on this branch and noticed that the following example is not fixed yet\r\nnot sure if it's a known but or not, but I'd expect `[FAIL. Reason: Assertion failed.] ` in this case\r\n```solidity\r\nfunction test_minimal() public {\r\n    reverter = new Reverter();\r\n    assertTrue(false);\r\n\r\n    vm.expectRevert();\r\n    reverter.doNotRevert();\r\n}\r\n[FAIL. Reason: Call did not revert as expected]\r\n```",
